    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行预计节日需求将推动经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/rbi-expects-festive-demand-in-india-to-help-revive-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行表示，节日期间需求复苏和消费者信心增强将推动该国放缓的经济，但警告称，中东地缘政治紧张局势可能威胁经济前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/rbi-expects-festive-demand-in-india-to-help-revive-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡隆称市场有点“糖高涨”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-21/markets-are-on-a-little-sugar-high-caron-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利投资管理公司跨资产解决方案首席信息官吉姆·卡隆表示，他并不看好市场，但我们正在非常非常快地实现软着陆。他正在接受“彭博监视”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-21/markets-are-on-a-little-sugar-high-caron-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科特迪瓦债券评级或将缩小与南非债券评级差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/ivory-coast-bonds-may-narrow-gap-to-south-africa-s-on-rating</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行策略师表示，标普全球上调科特迪瓦信用评级后，科特迪瓦与博茨瓦纳和毛里求斯一起，成为撒哈拉以南非洲评级最高的国家之一，这为其债券相对于南非的额外利差提供了缩小空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/ivory-coast-bonds-may-narrow-gap-to-south-africa-s-on-rating</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿曼 OQ 准备在 20 亿美元交易后几天再次进行 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/oman-s-oq-set-to-tee-up-another-ipo-days-after-2-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿曼国有能源公司 OQ SAOC 将于本月底启动其甲醇和液化石油气部门的首次公开募股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/oman-s-oq-set-to-tee-up-another-ipo-days-after-2-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:16:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌称新加坡海域有多达 40 吨污水泄漏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/shell-says-up-to-40-tons-of-slop-leaked-in-singapore-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司今天在一份声明中表示，陆上管道泄漏导致约 30 至 40 公吨的“油泥”——油和水的混合物——溢入新加坡附近海域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/shell-says-up-to-40-tons-of-slop-leaked-in-singapore-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 12:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称大都会人寿正在洽谈收购李嘉诚在中国境外的柏瑞资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/metlife-said-to-be-in-talks-to-buy-tycoon-li-s-pinebridge-assets-outside-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国保险公司大都会人寿保险公司 (MetLife Inc.) 正就收购 PineBridge Investments 在中国以外的资产进行深入谈判，交易价值可能为 10 亿至 15 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/metlife-said-to-be-in-talks-to-buy-tycoon-li-s-pinebridge-assets-outside-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 04:58:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>周末袭击后以色列计划下一步行动 油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国再次采取措施刺激经济，且交易商追踪中东紧张局势对供应造成的风险，油价在上周下跌逾 8% 后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 23:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
